snippet.title: Exploding Babies Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Exploding Babies is a quirky arena blaster coming to Steam early access 8/15/2019. Wishlist in Steam: http://bit.ly/WishlistinSteam

Trigger crazed drone babies to explode and take out the competition in a chain reaction. Up to 4 players competitive and co-op with crazy game modes for you and your friends.
